===Proper noun===
'''American'''  (''plural:'' '''[[Americans]]''')
# A person born in, or a [[citizen]] or [[inhabitant]] of, the [[United States of America]].
# An [[inhabitant]] of the [[America]]s. More often this is specified as either ''North American'' or ''South American.''

